-      set req.url = querystring.filter(req.url,
-                                       "q" + querystring.filtersep() + "p");
-
-regfilter
----------
-
-Prototype
-   STRING regfilter(STRING url, STRING parameter_names_regex)
-Description
-   Returns the given URI without the parameters matching a regular expression
