+set_string
+----------
+
+Prototype
+	set_string(STRING S, STRING T)
+        set(STRING S, STRING T) - shorthand
+Return value
+	NONE
+Description
+	Sets the variable identified by S to the value T.
+Example
+	var.set_string("bar", "some random string");
+
+get_string
+----------
+
+Prototype
+	get_string(STRING S)
