+There are similar functions named:
+
+* set_int(STRING, INT)
+* get_int(STRING)
+* set_real(STRING, REAL)
+* get_real(STRING)
+* set_duration(STRING, DURATION)
+* get_duration(STRING)
+
+get and set are shorthand for get_string and set_string.
